{"tid":2094047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街站掛「光時」橫額 警指違法一度沒收","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T09:44:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b78f2b78ce4db6e36972ebe5b1211afe5cb48b4","tid":2094047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/KYC7WZ5HGXMP6NILDNHG22CGHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FKYC7WZ5HGXMP6NILDNHG22CGHU%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=d76bde21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FKYC7WZ5HGXMP6NILDNHG22CGHU%2F&h=18639c72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200704/KYC7WZ5HGXMP6NILDNHG22CGHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n街站掛「光時」橫額 警指違法一度沒收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法實施後，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n天水連線數名<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n要求他們即時拆除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SEhDHDam2snLpHEp7qsKqjFn5bE=/190x116/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YR4JYZ2QENTH3SDW6TUC2BX2PI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSEhDHDam2snLpHEp7qsKqjFn5bE%3D%2F190x116%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYR4JYZ2QENTH3SDW6TUC2BX2PI.gif&h=d7866d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有警察昨日一度沒收街站寫上「光復香港，時代革命」的橫額，其後歸還。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促簽字條 天水連線拒絕<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被告多處骨折缺席聆訊<br />\n<br />\n成員將橫額除下，並一度遭警員沒收，警員其後將橫額歸還，其中一名警員遞上一張手寫字條，要求成員簽署，承認掛上一條寫有「光復香港，時代革命」的橫額，遭成員拒絕，並指橫額上標語為天水連線的理念。警員勸喻在場人士不要再展示有關橫額後離開。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議員岑敖暉與元朗區議員兼天水連線成員林進及伍建偉到場了解，林進指，多名政界及法律人士曾指，叫口號、舉標語不屬違反國安法，惟政府前晚卻突然發聲明指「光復香港，時代革命」有港獨、分離香港、顛覆國家政權等含意，批評做法不合理，擔心令市民自我設限。林進認為，有關口號象徵港人精神，呼籲抗爭人士不要畏縮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WAav7xK-17-0WZPhKh2-ESOMJ3E=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7FU24HCL7SEV7WZJ25JXFRSIF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWAav7xK-17-0WZPhKh2-ESOMJ3E%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7FU24HCL7SEV7WZJ25JXFRSIF4.gif&h=218ab8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天水連線成員昨呼籲抗爭人士不要畏縮。"},{"pid":"d3278697fc972c6bcf419554bcaec551ad13c713","tid":2094047,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"法就立左, 但好似冇一個執法標準，某強力部門冇order點做? 之前又話會重拳, 嚴刑........𨳒, 原來冇料到"},{"pid":"c322637d85f4fb477d58141eca42a47dc3ec4ac6","tid":2094047,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3278697fc972c6bcf419554bcaec551ad13c713","tid":2094047,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"法就立左, 但好似冇一個執法標準，某強力部門冇order點做? 之前又話會重拳, 嚴刑........𨳒, 原來冇料到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Up50NAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUp50NAe.jpg&h=3993e92c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}